---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="AI Automation Accelerator | Services">
<div class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-800 font-sans">
    <!-- Hero Section - Adapted for AI Automation -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-800 py-20 relative overflow-hidden">
        <!-- Background patterns (Adjusted colors and shapes) -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
            <div class="absolute top-20 left-20 w-40 h-40 transform rotate-45 bg-teal-400"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-20 right-20 w-60 h-60 transform -rotate-12 bg-blue-300"></div>
            <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/3 w-20 h-20 transform rotate-12 bg-yellow-300"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-7xl">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
                <div class="md:w-2/5 z-10">
                    <div class="inline-block bg-teal-500 text-white text-sm font-bold py-1 px-3 rounded-full mb-4">EFFICIENCY BOOST</div>
                    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4 leading-tight">AI Automation Accelerator</h1>
                    <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-blue-100 mb-6">Reclaim Your Time & Scale Smarter</h2>
                    <p class="text-white text-lg mb-8 max-w-xl">Stop drowning in manual tasks. We implement intelligent AI automations to handle repetitive work, boost efficiency, and free up your team for high-impact activities.</p>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
                        <a href="#contact" class="bg-teal-500 hover:bg-teal-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg transition duration-300 inline-flex items-center">
                            <span>Automate Your Business</span>
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                            </svg>
                        </a>
                        <a href="#how-it-works" class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-white hover:text-blue-700 transition duration-300">
                            See How It Works
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="md:w-3/5 mt-10 md:mt-0 z-10">
                    <img src="../images/ai-automation.png" alt="AI Automation Accelerator" class="rounded-lg shadow-xl w-full h-auto">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pain Points Section - Focused on Manual Work -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-6xl">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <span class="text-teal-500 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">FEELING OVERWHELMED?</span>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mt-2 mb-4">Buried Under Repetitive Tasks?</h2>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">Your business is growing, but manual processes are slowing you down and costing you valuable time.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300 border-t-4 border-teal-500 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                    <div class="text-teal-500 text-3xl mb-4">üò©</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">Drowning in Admin</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Too much time spent on data entry, scheduling, email management, and other low-value administrative tasks.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300 border-t-4 border-teal-500 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                    <div class="text-teal-500 text-3xl mb-4">üíæ</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">Manual Data Handling</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Constantly copying/pasting information between different apps, spreadsheets, and documents, leading to errors.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300 border-t-4 border-teal-500 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                    <div class="text-teal-500 text-3xl mb-4">‚è≥</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">Slow, Inefficient Processes</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Key workflows like onboarding, reporting, or follow-ups take too long because they rely on manual steps.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300 border-t-4 border-teal-500 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                    <div class="text-teal-500 text-3xl mb-4">ü§Ø</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">Team Burnout</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Your talented team is bogged down by tedious tasks instead of focusing on strategic work that drives growth.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300 border-t-4 border-teal-500 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                    <div class="text-teal-500 text-3xl mb-4">‚ùå</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">Costly Errors</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Manual processes inevitably lead to mistakes that cost time, money, and potentially damage client relationships.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300 border-t-4 border-teal-500 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                    <div class="text-teal-500 text-3xl mb-4">üìà</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">Scalability Blockers</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">You can't scale effectively because your current manual processes simply won't handle increased volume.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-16 text-center">
                <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">You don't need more staff to handle the busywork.</p>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-700">You need intelligent automation to work *for* you, 24/7.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How It Works Section - Automation Focused Process -->
    <section id="how-it-works" class="py-16 bg-white clip-diagonal-reverse relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-blue-100 clip-diagonal-reverse"></div>

        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-6xl relative z-10">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <span class="text-teal-500 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">OUR METHODOLOGY</span>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mt-2 mb-4">The 4-Phase AI Automation Journey</h2>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">We identify, design, and deploy high-impact AI automations tailored to your business.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-16">
                <!-- Phase 1: Discover -->
                <div class="relative">
                    <div class="absolute -left-4 -top-4 w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-teal-500 text-white text-xl font-bold flex items-center justify-center z-10">1</div>
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 h-full border-l-4 border-teal-500">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 mt-4">Discover</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">We dive deep into your current workflows to pinpoint the most impactful automation opportunities using our AI Readiness Assessment.</p>
                        <ul class="space-y-3">
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-teal-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                                <span>Workflow analysis & process mapping</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-teal-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                                <span>Identification of repetitive, time-consuming tasks</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-teal-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                                <span>Prioritization based on ROI and feasibility</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        <div class="text-teal-500 font-semibold mt-6">Week 1</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Phase 2: Design -->
                <div class="relative">
                    <div class="absolute -left-4 -top-4 w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-teal-500 text-white text-xl font-bold flex items-center justify-center z-10">2</div>
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 h-full border-l-4 border-teal-500">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 mt-4">Design</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">We architect intelligent automation solutions, selecting the right AI tools and designing seamless integrations with your existing systems.</p>
                        <ul class="space-y-3">
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-teal-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                                <span>Custom AI automation workflow blueprints</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-teal-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                                <span>AI tool selection & configuration planning</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-teal-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                                <span>Integration strategy with your tech stack</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        <div class="text-teal-500 font-semibold mt-6">Week 2</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Phase 3: Deploy -->
                <div class="relative">
                    <div class="absolute -left-4 -top-4 w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-teal-500 text-white text-xl font-bold flex items-center justify-center z-10">3</div>
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 h-full border-l-4 border-teal-500">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 mt-4">Deploy</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Our experts build, test, and implement the designed AI automations, ensuring they run smoothly and deliver the expected results.</p>
                        <ul class="space-y-3">
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-teal-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                                <span>Automation build & configuration</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-teal-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                                <span>Rigorous testing & quality assurance</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-teal-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                                <span>Phased rollout & monitoring</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        <div class="text-teal-500 font-semibold mt-6">Weeks 3-4+</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Phase 4: Drive -->
                <div class="relative">
                    <div class="absolute -left-4 -top-4 w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-teal-500 text-white text-xl font-bold flex items-center justify-center z-10">4</div>
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 h-full border-l-4 border-teal-500">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 mt-4">Drive</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">We empower your team to leverage the new automations effectively through training, documentation, and ongoing optimization support.</p>
                        <ul class="space-y-3">
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-teal-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                                <span>Team training on new AI tools & workflows</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-teal-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                                <span>Clear documentation & usage guides</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-teal-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                                <span>Performance monitoring & optimization roadmap</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        <div class="text-teal-500 font-semibold mt-6">Ongoing</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Automation Examples Section -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gray-900 text-white">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-6xl">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <span class="text-teal-400 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">WHAT WE AUTOMATE</span>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-2 mb-4">Unlock Efficiency Across Your Business</h2>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">We implement AI automations targeting key areas prone to manual work and bottlenecks.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <!-- Example 1: Email Management -->
                <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-8 border-l-4 border-teal-500 hover:bg-gray-700 transition duration-300">
                    <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" /></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">AI Email Assistant</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-gray-300">Automatically sort, prioritize, draft replies, and extract tasks from your inbox. Reach inbox zero faster.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- Example 2: Data Entry -->
                <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-8 border-l-4 border-teal-500 hover:bg-gray-700 transition duration-300">
                    <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 7h6m0 10v-3m-3 3h.01M9 17h.01M9 14h.01M12 14h.01M15 11h.01M12 11h.01M9 11h.01M7 21h10a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z" /></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Smart Data Entry</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-gray-300">Extract data from documents (invoices, forms, PDFs) and automatically populate spreadsheets or CRMs.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- Example 3: Reporting -->
                <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-8 border-l-4 border-teal-500 hover:bg-gray-700 transition duration-300">
                    <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 17v-2m3 2v-4m3 4v-6m2 10H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" /></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Automated Reporting</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-gray-300">Generate regular performance reports, summaries, and data visualizations automatically from various sources.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- Example 4: Customer Support -->
                <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-8 border-l-4 border-teal-500 hover:bg-gray-700 transition duration-300">
                    <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z" /></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">AI Support Agents</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-gray-300">Handle common customer inquiries instantly via chatbots or AI-assisted agent responses.</p>
                </div>
                 <!-- Example 5: Content Generation -->
                <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-8 border-l-4 border-teal-500 hover:bg-gray-700 transition duration-300">
                    <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h11a2 2 0 002-2v-5m-1.414-9.414a2 2 0 112.828 2.828L11.828 15H9v-2.828l8.586-8.586z" /></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Content Creation Engine</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-gray-300">Automate drafting of social media posts, email campaigns, blog outlines, and product descriptions.</p>
                </div>
                 <!-- Example 6: Task Management -->
                <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-8 border-l-4 border-teal-500 hover:bg-gray-700 transition duration-300">
                    <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4" /></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Smart Task Coordination</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-gray-300">Automatically create tasks, assign owners, set deadlines, and send reminders based on triggers or events.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-16 text-center">
                <a href="#contact" class="bg-teal-500 hover:bg-teal-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg transition duration-300 inline-flex items-center">
                    <span>Discover Your Automation Potential</span>
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Results Section - Automation Benefits -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-800 text-white relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
             <div class="absolute top-20 left-20 w-40 h-40 transform rotate-45 bg-teal-400"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-20 right-20 w-60 h-60 transform -rotate-12 bg-blue-300"></div>
            <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/3 w-20 h-20 transform rotate-12 bg-yellow-300"></div>
        </div>

